rows.label: kizunainn079_msg0001
rows.name:
I trust you're feeling refreshed!
I have a message for you.

rows.label: kizunainn079_msg0002
rows.name:
It said to bring Ten'i to Theospiti
Temple without delay.

rows.label: kizunainn079_msg0003
rows.name:
I didn't catch the name of
the man who left it. And
he cleared off sharpish too.
